Float32TC.name: Float32TC
Float32TC.description: This type represents a 32-bit (4-octet) IEEE floating-point number in binary interchange format.
Float32TC.reference: IEEE Standard for Floating-Point Arithmetic, Standard 754-2008

Float64TC.name: Float64TC
Float64TC.description: This type represents a 64-bit (8-octet) IEEE floating-point number in binary interchange format.
Float64TC.reference: IEEE Standard for Floating-Point Arithmetic, Standard 754-2008

Float128TC.name: Float128TC
Float128TC.description: This type represents a 128-bit (16-octet) IEEE floating-point number in binary interchange format.
Float128TC.reference: IEEE Standard for Floating-Point Arithmetic, Standard 754-2008
